@startuml Sequence_Recruiter_JobPosting
title Nhà Tuyển Dụng - Đăng Tin Tuyển Dụng

actor Recruiter as "👔 Recruiter"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant JobService as "Job\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Danh Sách Tin ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Tin tuyển dụng"
FrontEnd -> JobService: GET /api/jobs?recruiterId={id}&page=0&size=20
JobService -> Database: Query tin_tuyen_dung
Database --> JobService: Return list
JobService --> FrontEnd: Jobs list
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Hiển thị danh sách

== Tạo Tin Mới ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Đăng tin mới"
Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Nhập: tiêu đề, mô tả, số lương, địa điểm
FrontEnd -> JobService: POST /api/jobs\n(tieuDe, moTa, soLuong, mucLuong, diaDiem)
JobService -> Database: Create tin_tuyen_dung
Database --> JobService: Return jobId
JobService --> FrontEnd: Created
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: ✅ Đăng tin thành công

== Thêm Yêu Cầu Kỹ Năng ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Thêm kỹ năng"
FrontEnd -> JobService: GET /api/system-skills
JobService -> Database: Get all skills
Database --> JobService: Skills list
JobService --> FrontEnd: List
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Show dropdown

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Chọn kỹ năng & mức độ
FrontEnd -> JobService: POST /api/jobs/{jobId}/skills\n(skillId, mucYeuCau)
JobService -> Database: Create ct_ky_nang_tin
Database --> JobService: OK
JobService --> FrontEnd: Added
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: ✅ Thêm kỹ năng

== Thêm Địa Điểm ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Thêm khu vực"
FrontEnd -> JobService: GET /api/locations
JobService -> Database: Get all locations
Database --> JobService: Locations list
JobService --> FrontEnd: List
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Show dropdown

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Chọn khu vực
FrontEnd -> JobService: POST /api/jobs/{jobId}/locations\n(locationId)
JobService -> Database: Create ct_kv_tin
Database --> JobService: OK
JobService --> FrontEnd: Added
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: ✅ Thêm khu vực

== Cập Nhật & Đóng Tin ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Sửa"
Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Nhập dữ liệu mới
FrontEnd -> JobService: PUT /api/jobs/{jobId}
JobService -> Database: Update tin_tuyen_dung
Database --> JobService: OK
JobService --> FrontEnd: Updated
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: ✅ Cập nhật

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Đóng tin"
FrontEnd -> JobService: PATCH /api/jobs/{jobId}/close
JobService -> Database: Update status = CLOSED
Database --> JobService: OK
JobService --> FrontEnd: Closed
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: ✅ Đóng tin

@enduml
